        "action": "Introduce a new UK bank holiday to mark the day we went into lockdown",
        "additional_details": "We have all had to change our lives that day marks when everything changed for everyone across the country. How we all united to achieve one goal and in the future this day can be celebrated on how we go through this terrible period.",
